This directory is reserved for optional private libraries used only by this project.

Right now the project does not keep custom reusable libraries here because the firmware is split directly into modules under `src/` and `include/`.

Use `lib/` later if you want to extract parts of the project into standalone components, for example:
- an activity classifier library
- a step counter library
- a BLE service library
- utility code shared across multiple projects

If you add project-local libraries here, PlatformIO will compile and link them automatically.
